{"tid":1593895,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭雨盛點讚金義聖撐港人IG 遭大陸網民攻擊","createTime":"2019-09-25T09:37:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T11:02:29.000Z","uid":68738,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c4611f3b6abee7bfb9d860463b24d7e1ee2af832","tid":1593895,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T09:37:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190925/large/1569389370_5f2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190925%2Flarge%2F1569389370_5f2e.jpg&h=8b02c81d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人氣韓片《屍殺列車》的53歲男星金義聖，一直都非常關心香港「反送中」運動，除了在IG力撐港人外，他上周更跟韓國MBC新聞節目《探查企劃Straight》攝製隊襲港，實地採訪香港的示威情況。<br />\n<br />\n由於金義聖公開力撐港人，其IG一直遭到大陸網民留言攻擊，不過近日46歲型男鄭雨盛亦成為大陸網民炮轟的對象，事關他曾在IG點讚金義聖撐港人的相片，大陸網民紛紛留言批評鄭雨盛，表示：「不要亂點讚」、「你們國家政治一團亂，你還真有心」等，亦有網民稱以前很喜歡鄭雨盛，今後不會再支持他云云。<br />\n<br />\n鄭雨盛目前已取消所有對金義聖IG圖片的點讚，不過未知是否因為遭到大陸網民攻擊而影響心情，他今日在IG上載了一張全黑的圖片，而香港網民得知鄭雨盛被攻擊的事後，紛紛湧到其IG留言為他打氣，並感謝他支持香港。<br />\n<br />\n其實，鄭雨盛已非首名因點讚金義聖撐港人IG相片而被大陸網民攻擊的韓星，韓劇《愛上Pinocchio》男星尹均相早前亦被發現曾點讚金義聖的圖片，同樣遭到大陸網民攻擊，批評尹均相支持香港示威者，事後尹均相取消讚好，並透過IG留言道歉，不過大陸網民仍未有停止對他的攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190925/60082627\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190925%2F60082627&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9FwLDRbgpiba54y0vEBNjMo%3D&h=3ecf29ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190925%2F60082627&h=f688435a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190925/60082627</a>"},{"pid":"ce34aac7f61940569caa8910e4d76e79c8523163","tid":1593895,"uid":2360,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T09:39:17.000Z","msg":"支那人真係好失禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c2c902ed6a10c3b3468a8908fd7e1c2801f0b2","tid":1593895,"uid":16087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T09:55:45.000Z","msg":"冇記錯佢係黎明個fd黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d96169ec3c0636daf826a5b49221b8f8f17eb0","tid":1593895,"uid":64476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:02:05.000Z","msg":"金義聖好似係佢旗下藝人"},{"pid":"0199feca3e2cddbdb85badb6a8ea1805ee1fd665","tid":1593895,"uid":4728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T11:02:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}